# Mobile agent rules

## Frame analysis concurrency

Only **one** `POST /analyze-frame` request may be **in flight** at a time. Queue or drop frames coherently; never stack concurrent calls. Wait for response or terminal error before sending the next frame.

## Contracts

Import shared types from `@roadcopilot/contracts`. Do not duplicate `AnalyzeFrame*`, `TripEvent`, `RouteOption`, or `FamilySummary` shapes locally—extend the package if fields are missing (then coordinate with contracts owner).

## Sensors

Hard brake, rapid acceleration, and sharp swerve logic runs **on-device**. Keep thresholds tunable and log-friendly for demo tuning.

## Replay / demo

Support **replay/demo** using `POST /analyze-video-replay` when live camera is unavailable. Label the experience clearly so it is not mistaken for a live trip.
